abstract: >-
  Kal Alien Mathematics is a formally verified mathematical framework that
  explores algebraic structures, complexity bounds, and topological limits
  beyond anthropocentric mathematical aesthetics. All core theorems are
  machine-checked by the Lean 4 kernel (v4.14.0) with zero axiom declarations.
  The Hilbert Agent v2.1 provides automated proof synthesis using LeanBERT,
  Gemini 2.5 Flash, and DeepSeek-Prover-V2-7B. Invented by Xavier Callens
  as a hybrid Human-AI mathematical discovery.
